============
Notes
============
This file has some important notes about decisions made during the development of NfQuery.


 * 24 September 2011 - 20:13
   MySQL INNODB transaction model has autocommit enabled by default. So in database class when we create a database connection instance we also set the autocommit disabled. Then we catch the exceptions if any error happens. Finally, we commit the queries into database
   before closing the connection. 

